iaik.pdf.asn1objects

Class SpUserNotice

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
      • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.SpUserNotice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type

    public class SpUserNotice
extends SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
    This class represents the signature policy qualifier of type sp-user-notice. It contains a user notice that should be displayed whenever the signature is validated.
